"ES\", \"productType\": \"PHYSICAL\", \"transactionType\": \"B2C\", \"netAmount\": 300.0, \"currency\": \"EUR\", \"chargedTaxAmount\": 48.0 },\n    { \"id\": \"h-020\", \"sellerCountry\": \"BR\", \"buyerCountry\": \"BR\", \"productType\": \"PHYSICAL\", \"transactionType\": \"B2C\", \"netAmount\": 1000.0, \"currency\": \"BRL\", \"chargedTaxAmount\": 160.0 }\n  ]\n}"
